# Halaman Dashboard

## Struktur folder (halaman kompleks)

```
app/(dashboard)/{modul}/{role}/{fitur}/
  page.tsx              # komposisi tipis, "use client"
  types.ts              # tipe UI / response API
  hooks/use{Fitur}.ts   # fetch, state, handler
  components/
    index.ts            # barrel export
    {Fitur}Table.tsx
    {Fitur}Filters.tsx
    {Fitur}Skeleton.tsx
  utils.tsx             # format tanggal, badge (re-export dari lib jika perlu)
```

Halaman sederhana boleh satu `page.tsx`; halaman list/laporan wajib pecah hook + components.

## Layout wajib

```tsx
"use client"

import { DashboardLayout, FilterSummaryPanel, PageActions, ContentEmpty } from "@/components/layout"

export default function MyPage() {
  return (
    <DashboardLayout title="Judul Halaman">
      <div className="space-y-4">
        {/* konten */}
      </div>
    </DashboardLayout>
  )
}
```

| Kebutuhan | Komponen |
|-----------|----------|
| Tombol aksi kanan header | `<PageActions>` |
| Filter + ringkasan | `<FilterSummaryPanel>` + `<CompactFilterCard>` |
| Section dengan judul | `<PageSection title="..." action={...}>` |
| Kartu form/konten | `<SectionCard title="...">` |
| Kosong | `<ContentEmpty title="..." description="..." />` |
| Loading | `<Skeleton />` atau komponen `*Skeleton` |

Filter: `FilterField`, `FILTER_GRID_CLASS`, `FILTER_CONTROL_CLASS` dari `@/components/layout`.

## Tabel & aksi

- Bungkus tabel: `<TableContainer><Table>...</Table></TableContainer>`
- Aksi baris: **ikon + tooltip**, bukan tombol teks panjang:

```tsx
import { TableActionLink, TableActionButton, TableActions } from "@/components/ui/table-actions"
import { Eye } from "lucide-react"

<TableCell className="text-right">
  <TableActionLink label="Detail" icon={Eye} href={`/path/${id}`} />
</TableCell>
```

- Badge status: ekstrak ke `lib/{modul}/` atau `utils.tsx` halaman.

## Data & performa

- Client **fetch ke API route**, jangan query Prisma langsung.
- List besar: pagination/filter di **server** (query params `page`, `start_date`, dll.).
- Default filter periode: awal bulan → hari ini (lihat `getDefaultPermintaanGroupDateRange`).
- State loading / empty / data eksplisit; feedback error pakai `toast` dari `sonner`.

## Detail halaman

- `[id]/page.tsx` atau `detail/page.tsx` + `useSearchParams` untuk query (`unit`, `tgl`).
- Tombol kembali: `<Button variant="ghost" size="sm" asChild><Link href="...">Kembali</Link></Button>`
